<plot>John G. G. Tucker, the most dangerous cockroach around, is hanging out at a gas station in the lonely Arizona desert. John is dead sure he is the best. But he hasn't heard of Hessi James, the little bug, yet # and underrating him will be Tucker's undoing. When Hessi drives up with his old Plymouth Convertible to fill up, John regards this as a provocation and picks a quarrel. But Hessi isn't the taciturn type and when he starts talking he'll never stop... "Hessi James" is the screen adaptation of a well-known sketch by the Hessian comedy duo Badesalz - making a comic highlight of this very funny story by imaginative and pointed animation.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?237575</url></doc>
